# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:15
translate portuguese juliana3_d10e8604:

    # "I sit down and start studying with Juliana."
    "Sento-me e começo a estudar com a Juliana."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:18
translate portuguese juliana3_b74be5eb:

    # "A few minutes into working on my essay for English class, I catch a glimpse of her staring at me."
    "Passados alguns minutos a trabalhar na minha redação para a aula de Inglês, vejo-a a olhar para mim."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:23
translate portuguese juliana3_e3606a98:

    # "I keep on working, and eventually she goes back to looking at her computer, but has a strange smile on her face."
    "Continuo a trabalhar e, eventualmente, ela volta a olhar para o computador, mas tem um sorriso estranho no rosto."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:25
translate portuguese juliana3_467078e7:

    # "I look up at her."
    "Olho para ela."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:28
translate portuguese juliana3_dbd19896:

    # "She immediately turns away, embarrassed."
    "Ela vira-se imediatamente, envergonhada."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:29
translate portuguese juliana3_c8017a7f:

    # pc "Did you need something?"
    pc "Precisavas de alguma coisa?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:30
translate portuguese juliana3_cbe6926b:

    # bn "Oh, um, yes."
    bn "Oh, hum, sim."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:32
translate portuguese juliana3_3f6b775b:

    # bn "I just wanted to ask you what you thought about the short story we were supposed to read for the next test?"
    bn "Só queria perguntar-te o que achaste do conto que devíamos ler para o próximo teste?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:33
translate portuguese juliana3_81a81d72:

    # bn "\"The Lottery,\" by Shirley Jackson?"
    bn "«The Lottery», de Shirley Jackson?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:34
translate portuguese juliana3_fef12cf2:

    # bn "Did you read it yet?"
    bn "Já o leste?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:37
translate portuguese juliana3_376a98f7:

    # pc "Yeah, I thought it was really messed up."
    pc "Sim, achei que era mesmo perturbador."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:39
translate portuguese juliana3_338df114:

    # bn "Right?"
    bn "Não achas?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:40
translate portuguese juliana3_bfd59367:

    # bn "But I loved it. I thought it really spoke to how things are today in the world with cancel-culture and hive-think."
    bn "Mas adorei. Achei que refletia mesmo como as coisas estão hoje no mundo, com a cultura do cancelamento e o pensamento de colmeia."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:41
translate portuguese juliana3_bec7d038:

    # pc "Absolutely. The way society seems to choose a person almost at random every couple of months to just destroy."
    pc "Sem dúvida. A forma como a sociedade parece escolher uma pessoa quase ao acaso a cada dois meses para simplesmente a destruir."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:43
translate portuguese juliana3_2fe4098b:

    # bn "Exactly! Shirley Jackson seemed to notice this even back in the pre-Twitter days of the 1940's and we're still doing the same thing today."
    bn "Exatamente! A Shirley Jackson parece ter percebido isto mesmo nos tempos pré-Twitter da década de 1940 e continuamos a fazer a mesma coisa hoje em dia."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:44
translate portuguese juliana3_d42061c8:

    # bn "It's kind of crazy when you think about how little we've changed in nearly 80 years."
    bn "É um pouco louco quando pensamos no quão pouco mudámos em quase 80 anos."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:46
translate portuguese juliana3_4978b7b3:

    # pc "Yeah, I read it."
    pc "Sim, li-o."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:48
translate portuguese juliana3_aa3188bb:

    # bn "What did you think about it?"
    bn "O que achaste?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:49
translate portuguese juliana3_42049acb:

    # pc "It was good. It was really cool when the person won the lottery."
    pc "Foi bom. Foi muito fixe quando a pessoa ganhou a lotaria."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:51
translate portuguese juliana3_9f337d9f:

    # bn "It was cool when they chose a person at random and then stoned them in the middle of the town?"
    bn "Foi fixe quando escolheram uma pessoa ao acaso e depois a apedrejaram no meio da cidade?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:52
translate portuguese juliana3_5bb78b12:

    # pc "Wait, what?"
    pc "Espera, o quê?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:53
translate portuguese juliana3_5a363cf3:

    # bn "You didn't read it."
    bn "Tu não leste."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:54
translate portuguese juliana3_0c160447:

    # pc "I didn't read it."
    pc "Não li."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:55
translate portuguese juliana3_5a937e4f:

    # bn "Well you should. It's really interesting and not that long. Plus, you know... grades."
    bn "Bem, devias ler. É muito interessante e não é assim tão longo. Além disso, sabes... notas."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:58
translate portuguese juliana3_13efba33:

    # bn "Oh okay. Well I think you might like it."
    bn "Ah, está bem. Bem, acho que podes gostar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:59
translate portuguese juliana3_906d25f8:

    # bn "I thought it was great. It's kind of crazy how much this story she wrote in the 1940s is still relevant today."
    bn "Achei fantástico. É um pouco louco como esta história que ela escreveu na década de 1940 ainda é relevante hoje em dia."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:60
translate portuguese juliana3_3a967afc:

    # bn "It made me think a lot about cancel-culture and hive-think and traditions. It's really interesting."
    bn "Fez-me pensar muito sobre a cultura do cancelamento, o pensamento de grupo e as tradições. É mesmo interessante."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:61
translate portuguese juliana3_c617b9bc:

    # pc "Well now I'm really looking forward to checking it out."
    pc "Bem, agora estou mesmo ansioso por dar uma vista de olhos."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:63
translate portuguese juliana3_6af83129:

    # "We went back to studying a little bit, until it was time to go to class."
    "Voltámos a estudar um pouco, até chegar a hora de ir para a aula."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:65
translate portuguese juliana3_a3b2a8a1:

    # bn "I'm really enjoying these morning study sessions, [pcname]. I hope they're helpful to you."
    bn "Estou a gostar muito destas sessões de estudo matinais, [pcname]. Espero que te sejam úteis."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:66
translate portuguese juliana3_27133e98:

    # pc "Oh they definitely are. I'm enjoying them too."
    pc "Oh, sem dúvida que são. Também estou a gostar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:68
translate portuguese juliana3_4db47928:

    # bn "Good, I'm glad."
    bn "Ótimo, fico contente."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:69
translate portuguese juliana3_564926ab:

    # bn "Maybe we could do more um, studying sometime."
    bn "Talvez pudéssemos fazer mais... estudar, um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:72
translate portuguese juliana3_1bcf3ec2:

    # bn "Me too."
    bn "Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:73
translate portuguese juliana3_42a0f7ac:

    # bn "Okay, I'll see you in class, [pcname]."
    bn "Ok, vejo-te na aula, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:74
translate portuguese juliana3_2f9bd46c:

    # bn "Bye."
    bn "Adeus."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:77
translate portuguese juliana3_99274675:

    # bn "No, I just mean studying."
    bn "Não, refiro-me apenas a estudar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:78
translate portuguese juliana3_3b72cdbb:

    # bn "Not a date, nothing like that, just studying."
    bn "Não é um encontro, nada disso, apenas estudar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:79
translate portuguese juliana3_b7f25017:

    # bn "I should go, I'll see you in class."
    bn "Tenho de ir, vejo-te na aula."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:80
translate portuguese juliana3_be151bf5:

    # bn "Bye"
    bn "Adeus"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:83
translate portuguese juliana3_f4127d98:

    # bn "What do you mean?"
    bn "O que queres dizer?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:84
translate portuguese juliana3_9c299014:

    # bn "Are you talking about sex stuff?"
    bn "Estás a falar de coisas de sexo?"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:85
translate portuguese juliana3_dd64a4d7:

    # bn "That's not at all what I was thinking about."
    bn "Não era nada disso que eu estava a pensar."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:86
translate portuguese juliana3_61af0dfb:

    # bn "Just studying, that's all."
    bn "Só a estudar, é tudo."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:88
translate portuguese juliana3_5e33a611:

    # bn "I should go. I'll see you in class."
    bn "Tenho de ir. Vejo-te na aula."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:89
translate portuguese juliana3_2f9bd46c_1:

    # bn "Bye."
    bn "Adeus."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:92
translate portuguese juliana3_9dbe4ff7:

    # "She immediately packs up all of her things and rushes off out of the café, her face turning red."
    "Ela arruma imediatamente todas as suas coisas e sai apressadamente do café, com o rosto a ficar vermelho."

# game/Scenes/Juliana/juliana3.rpy:93
translate portuguese juliana3_d69c9faa:

    # "I wait just a bit, then pack up my things as well and head to class."
    "Espero um pouco, depois arrumo as minhas coisas também e vou para a aula."

